Class OrganizationViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
      • androidx.lifecycle.AndroidViewModel
        • edu.cnm.deepdive.tvnclient.viewmodel.OrganizationViewModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DefaultLifecycleObserver, LifecycleObserver
    public class OrganizationViewModel
extends AndroidViewModel
implements DefaultLifecycleObserver
    Prepares and manages the data for the Organization, SearchOrganizationFragment and Opportunity fragment . Handles the communication of the Organization, SearchOrganizationFragment and Opportunitywith the rest of the application.
